We can remove the warning message or at the least change it to debug level.

Update - When there are no reporters registered when creating a metrics registry, none of the metrics will be reported. Hence, add a default Jmx reporter when there are no reporters registered. Also, log a warning if reporters are added after some metrics have been registered as they might be lost due to new metrics registry.

